title: Thursday Sector Leaders: Apparel Stores, Auto Parts - Nasdaq.com
text: In trading on Thursday, apparel stores shares were relative leaders, up on the day by about 4.6%. Leading the group were shares of Lands' End, up about 17.7% and shares of American Eagle Outfitters, up about 10.8% on the day.    makeArticleAd();  Also showing relative strength are auto parts shares, up on the day by about 4.6% as a group, led by Adient, trading up by about 15.1% and Tenneco, trading up by about 13.8% on Thursday.
